{"tid":2107611,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"梁美芬指民主派初選或違基本法　冀政府嚴肅跟進","createTime":"2020-07-14T03:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T04:57:51.000Z","uid":104865,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"00e405711b9a2520e4891b9cc52ea4121b713f21","tid":2107611,"uid":104865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:56:22.000Z","msg":"經民聯立法會議員梁美芬認為，政府必須嚴肅跟進民主派初選，質疑初選是為協調以癱瘓立法會為目標的民主派「35+」行動，有可能違反《基本法》。<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬指，初選為爭取立法會議席過半而舉行，當中有參選人表明一定否決財政預算案，以癱瘓立法會及香港，爭取訴求，會帶來嚴重政治後果，令人憂慮。政府亦要調查初選有否違反《港區國安法》第22條。<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬又表示，民主派初選大規模號召投票，而且不同地區都有票站，<span class=\"red\">誤導普通市民以為屬正式選舉。她指有市民向建制派議員求助，以為初選等於正式選舉，詢問如何投票。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人一藍 腦便殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:  <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537616-20200714.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537616-20200714.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCn9ey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=c9df2935\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537616-20200714.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=51d84d8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537616-20200714.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"18a719fc259e729cd37ccadc407c19f560725d85","tid":2107611,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T04:00:07.000Z","msg":"巧京<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00bd3c5f8f22aa312fce95b5bf55602875b3bc3","tid":2107611,"uid":335303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T04:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/214tp39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F214tp39.jpg&h=e74a1db8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65871e1fb7c785b2498554d9